text: <@U0W7D64LC|markparz> uploaded a file: <https://hyperledgerproject.slack.com/files/markparz/F2KABTPA5/using_jira.docx|Using_Jira.docx> and commented: Hi everyone, this might be pretty widely known information, however I’ve had questions come in regarding Jira, how to maneuver to easily see a prioritized list of items by endorser, consenter(orderer), ledger, etc. <@U1KDHJT6H> (thank you) did a great job of creating public boards to help people see what we believe are the highest priority items. I put this doc together to assist in navigation to these boards.  I also ask if there is something out of priority, or something you feel is a higher priority item, please bring it up here in this slack channel. I’m working to keep the list in order as best I can, but need your feedback as well to help rank these.
